    "description": "The paper introduces a comprehensive survey bridging deep learning and mobile and wireless networking research. It covers essential background on deep learning techniques and their potential applications in networking, discusses several techniques and platforms that facilitate the efficient deployment of deep learning onto mobile systems, and provides an encyclopedic review of existing mobile and wireless networking research based on deep learning, categorized by different domains. Furthermore, it addresses how to tailor deep learning specifically for mobile environments, concluding with current challenges and open future directions for research.",
